            <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Control de stock en tiempo real, alertas de bajo inventario, ajustes, transferencias entre negocios.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-xl border border-gray-100 p-6 transition hover:border-violeta/30 hover:shadow-sm">
            <div class="mb-3 flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-violeta/10"><svg class="h-5 w-5 text-violeta" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8c-1.657 0-3 .895-3 2s1.343 2 3 2 3 .895 3 2-1.343 2-3 2m0-8c1.11 0 2.08.402 2.599 1M12 8V7m0 1v8m0 0v1m0-1c-1.11 0-2.08-.402-2.599-1M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" /></svg></div>
            <h3 class="mb-2 font-bold">Multimoneda</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Conversión automática, tasas personalizables, cierres por moneda. Ideal para economías dolarizadas.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-xl border border-gray-100 p-6 transition hover:border-violeta/30 hover:shadow-sm">
            <div class="mb-3 flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-violeta/10"><svg class="h-5 w-5 text-violeta" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 4.354a4 4 0 110 5.292M15 21H3v-1a6 6 0 0112 0v1zm0 0h6v-1a6 6 0 00-9-5.197m13.5-9a2.25 2.25 0 11-4.5 0 2.25 2.25 0 014.5 0z" /></svg></div>
            <h3 class="mb-2 font-bold">Roles y permisos</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Define accesos por usuario: cajero, supervisor, administrador, contador. Control granular de cada acción.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-xl border border-gray-100 p-6 transition hover:border-violeta/30 hover:shadow-sm">
            <div class="mb-3 flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-violeta/10"><svg class="h-5 w-5 text-violeta" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 9V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2h2m2 4h10a2 2 0 002-2v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H9a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2zm7-5a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0z" /></svg></div>
            <h3 class="mb-2 font-bold">Créditos y cobranzas</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Administración de créditos, cuentas por cobrar, intereses por mora, notificaciones automáticas de pago.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-xl border border-gray-100 p-6 transition hover:border-violeta/30 hover:shadow-sm">
            <div class="mb-3 flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-violeta/10"><svg class="h-5 w-5 text-violeta" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 19v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2zm0 0V9a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v10m-6 0a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v14a2 2 0 01-2 2h-2a2 2 0 01-2-2z" /></svg></div>
            <h3 class="mb-2 font-bold">Reportes</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Dashboard en tiempo real, reportes de ventas, comisiones, impuestos, rentabilidad. Exporta a PDF/CSV.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-xl border border-gray-100 p-6 transition hover:border-violeta/30 hover:shadow-sm">
            <div class="mb-3 flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-violeta/10"><svg class="h-5 w-5 text-violeta" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 11H5m14 0a2 2 0 012 2v6a2 2 0 01-2 2H5a2 2 0 01-2-2v-6a2 2 0 012-2m14 0V9a2 2 0 00-2-2M5 11V9a2 2 0 012-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h6a2 2 0 012 2v2M7 7h10" /></svg></div>
            <h3 class="mb-2 font-bold">Suscripciones</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Facturación recurrente, recordatorios de pago, control de vencimientos, múltiples pasarelas de pago.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-xl border border-gray-100 p-6 transition hover:border-violeta/30 hover:shadow-sm">
            <div class="mb-3 flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-violeta/10"><svg class="h-5 w-5 text-violeta" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z" /></svg></div>
            <h3 class="mb-2 font-bold">Onboarding</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Configuración guiada paso a paso. Asistente de migración de datos, importación masiva desde Excel/CSV.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- PAÍSES -->
    <section id="paises" class="bg-gray-50 px-4 py-20">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl">
        <h2 class="mb-4 text-center text-3xl font-bold">Disponible en toda Latinoamérica</h2>
        <p class="mb-12 text-center text-gray-600">Cobertura fiscal regional con actualización constante</p>
        <div class="mb-12 flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-8">
          {countries.map(c => (
            <div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-1">
              <span class={`fi fi-${c.code} h-10 w-10 rounded-full shadow-sm`}></span>
              <span class="text-xs font-medium text-gray-600">{c.name}</span>
            </div>
          ))}
        </div>
        <div class="grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3">
          {countryFiscalInfo.map(cf => (
            <div class="flex items-start gap-4 rounded-xl bg-white p-5 shadow-sm">
              <span class={`fi fi-${cf.flag} mt-0.5 h-8 w-8 flex-shrink-0 rounded-full`}></span>
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-bold">{cf.title}</h4>
                <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">{cf.desc}</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          ))}
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- PLANES -->
    <section id="planes" class="px-4 py-20">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl">
        <h2 class="mb-4 text-center text-3xl font-bold">Planes flexibles</h2>
        <p class="mb-12 text-center text-gray-600">Elige el plan que mejor se adapte a tu negocio. Cambia cuando quieras.</p>
        <div class="grid gap-8 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4">
          {plans.map(p => (
            <div class={`relative flex flex-col rounded-2xl border p-6 ${p.popular ? 'border-violeta shadow-xl shadow-violeta/10' : 'border-gray-200'} ${p.premium ? 'bg-gradient-to-br from-gray-900 via-gray-900 to-violeta-900 text-white' : 'bg-white'}`}>
              {p.popular && <span class="absolute -top-3 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 rounded-full bg-violeta px-4 py-1 text-xs font-bold text-white">Popular</span>}
              <h3 class={`mb-1 text-xl font-bold ${p.premium ? 'text-white' : ''}`}>{p.name}</h3>
              <p class={`mb-4 text-sm ${p.premium ? 'text-gray-300' : 'text-gray-500'}`}>{p.desc}</p>
              <div class="mb-5">
                {p.price === 'Custom' ? (
                  <span class={`text-3xl font-extrabold ${p.premium ? 'text-white' : ''}`}>A medida</span>
                ) : (
                  <>
                    <span class={`text-4xl font-extrabold ${p.premium ? 'text-white' : ''}`}>{p.price}</span>
                    <span class={`text-sm ${p.premium ? 'text-gray-300' : 'text-gray-500'}`}>/mes</span>
                  </>
                )}
              </div>
              <ul class="mb-6 flex-1 space-y-3">
